<view class="screen wrongbook-screen">
  <z-bg></z-bg>
  <z-page-head kicker="FEEDBACK" title="课后反馈" desc="老师上传图片、文字和语音，学生/家长查看课后反馈。"></z-page-head>

  <view class="grid-3 wrong-stats">
    <view><z-metric value="4" label="反馈样例"></z-metric></view>
    <view><z-metric value="3" label="图片素材"></z-metric></view>
    <view><z-metric value="3" label="语音素材"></z-metric></view>
  </view>

  <view class="chip-row filter-row">
    <z-chip text="全部" active="{{true}}"></z-chip>
    <z-chip text="生物"></z-chip>
    <z-chip text="数学"></z-chip>
    <z-chip text="英语"></z-chip>
  </view>

  <z-card mode="light">
    <view class="wrong-head">
      <view>
        <text class="wrong-subject">初三生物1班 · 第一次课</text>
        <text class="wrong-title">细胞结构复习反馈</text>
      </view>
      <z-status text="已反馈"></z-status>
    </view>
    <view class="wrong-body">老师已上传批改照片和语音说明，家长可查看图片并收听语音。</view>
  </z-card>

  <z-card mode="light">
    <view class="wrong-head">
      <view>
        <text class="wrong-subject">初二数学A班 · 第一次课</text>
        <text class="wrong-title">一次函数图像反馈</text>
      </view>
      <z-status text="已反馈"></z-status>
    </view>
    <view class="wrong-body">本页是历史入口兼容展示，主流程请进入“老师反馈”。</view>
  </z-card>

  <z-card>
    <z-section-title title="当前主流程" right="手机号登录"></z-section-title>
    <view class="body-copy">老师从课程课次进入学生名单上传课后反馈；学生/家长用报班手机号查看。</view>
  </z-card>
</view>
